to específico","guid":"2q4ICaJIRiyS7-djU21C0Q","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"128","text":"Observación durante episodio (idealmente 4-8h)","guid":"JesEQa9CSS2QTdqsIT0FZQ","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"128","text":"Monitorización signos vitales","guid":"NV3iEtdUTPeAygy9ZWpfGQ","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"128","text":"Reevaluar periódicamente función cognitiva","guid":"0nqINe95QViL_nYGHSiMbQ","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"128","text":"Acompañamiento → reducir ansiedad del paciente","guid":"GR_C8Nf0TTyxHDxqMImBFg","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"128","text":"NO administrar benzodiazepinas ni anticoagulantes","guid":"FBE2NqsZRzKN50Pkh36t0g","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"128","text":"NO iniciar antiagregantes por AGT aislada","guid":"QFxwEpE6Reef8hvbXvHcVQ","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"128","text":"Alta segura si resolución completa y examen neurológico normal","guid":"1l6E4LMBRjSAVfb0nKdedA","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"128","text":"Indicar RM ambulatoria (24-48h post-inicio → ventana óptima)","guid":"RJwestOKS-e1XMvvsdsXmg","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"128","text":"Derivar a neurología si atípico o duda diagnóstica","guid":"wAXu45nTTiKS72gzM5J8Kw","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones\\NGeriátricas","guid":"x_7Et9akRVa7zC6UbD2MZQ","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"Diagnóstico diferencial más\\Namplio en adulto mayor","guid":"E-8pdlqcTqCcWF6Cw1Zz4A","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"Mayor prevalencia de AIT, ACV, demencia incipiente","guid":"6ecCSXSsRoC4BUWQzlF-lg","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"Delirium hipoactivo puede simular amnesia","guid":"o76VqpLpRf2BsRtJYdl7Qw","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"139","text":"Evaluación cognitiva\\Nbasal importante","guid":"bOjjJ-rTQ6CeHNTEgDWJVA","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"MoCA o MMSE post-resolución → descartar deterioro previo","guid":"MDbdrVwrSgS_Lgeyo5PX5A","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"Si rendimiento subnormal → estudio cognitivo ambulatorio","guid":"frOmfI_7SJWlFcVt8BRBTw","children":[]}]},{"id":"146","parent":"139","text":"Factores de riesgo vascular\\Nfrecuentes → no implican AIT","guid":"YsB8WItHS8CQLqCJ0oDMQg","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"AGT NO es equivalente isquémico","guid":"lBQefxCDS1moSkY-U4lwuQ","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"NO requiere estudio vascular extenso si presentación típica","guid":"fZ_3y3eeTqmNTWQLBODfUg","children":[]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"139","text":"Fármacos anticolinérgicos → descartar como contribuyentes","guid":"jJETMSrjSfuQxNwBUPy-JA","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"139","text":"Valorar fragilidad → impacto en ansiedad post-episodio","guid":"Un55vhdVRA-j2mRhoZYxYQ","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"139","text":"Polifarmacia → revisar si benzodiazepinas u opioides contribuyen","guid":"v_81eBAgQ6y3XHC57Tdc8A","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"139","text":"Educar familia → episodio benigno, baja recurrencia","guid":"fo6ne461RqiaAczq6yTRqg","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"139","text":"Riesgo de diagnóstico erróneo de demencia → AGT NO es demencia","guid":"rzDc6RclS8miTSa3FqWYgQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"154","parent":"0","text":"Pronóstico y\\NSeguimiento","guid":"bEiQpVCeSQin7stWbGUJVA","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"Resolución completa habitual en <24h","guid":"J5eREbs7SdSFzcMKPrSlZQ","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"154","text":"Brecha amnésica permanente → normal, no implica daño persistente","guid":"Ww8uRYWBSiu8sBVEuq0cmw","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"154","text":"Recurrencia 6-10% → bajo riesgo","guid":"AQtUhB0gQl6BywgHkcNDrw","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"154","text":"Sin aumento riesgo de ACV o demencia","guid":"gviDsMcwSYCv8XS0IkBuUw","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"154","text":"Datos recientes sugieren\\Nperfil más complejo","guid":"xSCmYfuxQkKRL-Yyb0snWA","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"Déficits sutiles de memoria a largo plazo en algunos pacientes","guid":"jW8WQBAKQdCIPSeA7IjPJA","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"Posible asociación con deterioro cognitivo subjetivo","guid":"Zjs9BSOuTkmvXuFZIkHFbQ","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"Necesidad de seguimiento cognitivo en investigación","guid":"9RIRKsGxSfaFgY56CI_pnA","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"154","text":"Calidad de vida → generalmente no afectada","guid":"-yi4SCNGT_WlYJygX4nMQQ","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"154","text":"No requiere restricción de actividades post-episodio","guid":"cAHA7XT9TrePV7JV0tpEpw","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"154","text":"Conducción → puede reanudarse tras resolución completa","guid":"TaemO32uTh2bI35AAay-4A","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClínicas","guid":"5lyAl61JQuqTybNMvINkDA","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"Preguntas repetitivas = signo cardinal → pensar AGT si >50 años, inicio agudo, sin focalidad","guid":"Rx05wqHiQLGTu6K4nrbZ1A","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"RM entre 24-48h post-inicio → ventana óptima para detectar lesión CA1","guid":"t2sPBjhgS0S7rngtQvPgUg","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"166","text":"HDR en RM puede ser OMITIDA en informes → revisar DWI personalmente","guid":"mOLuwQXiToaTh8uSrmL0iA","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"166","text":"AGT NO es AIT → no iniciar antiagregación ni anticoagulación","guid":"TuAwu_OrSbu6qrUnoThQlA","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"166","text":"Actividad sexual como desencadenante → preguntar activamente (subregistro)","guid":"tYwgqS_KRby5CASevDK6HA","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"166","text":"Si episodios breves, recurrentes, al despertar → pensar AET, no AGT","guid":"Vdf5goKZTxyF718keUMDLw","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"166","text":"Pérdida de identidad personal = NO es AGT → pensar amnesia disociativa","guid":"9Eell1E-QHSbWWrA3aXJ_Q","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"166","text":"Adulto mayor con amnesia aguda → descartar delirium hipoactivo PRIMERO","guid":"ZeAGiVsWS6yNNyZ8Lok2Qg","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"166","text":"No confundir con demencia incipiente → evaluación cognitiva post-resolución","guid":"a6x6gPopSheP4IzXlldZ-Q","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"166","text":"Tranquilizar al paciente y familia → pronóstico excelente, recurrencia baja","guid":"SDpYMCQiTVa1R-plZdegog","children":[]}]},{"id":"177","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"FyP5hNBQTJaixEj0BQfTbA","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"1. Ropper AH. Transient Global Amnesia. N Engl J Med. 2023;388(7):635-640.","guid":"ncbDIH5ZRTSaY9NO3wtdjA","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"177","text":"2. Miller TD, Butler CR. Acute-onset amnesia: TGA and other causes. Pract Neurol. 2022;22(3):201-208.","guid":"EwHxCLMkRFOqgA1n7Us7lA","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"177","text":"3. Galwa-Støkkan AK, et al. Transient global amnesia. Tidsskr Nor Laegeforen. 2025;145(13).","guid":"w_SykuwFTweMF0xiXZE4Ew","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"177","text":"4. Marazzi C, et al. Transient global amnesia. Acta Biomed. 2014;85(3):229-35.","guid":"bgdrNfAuSC-F6-YvSNKZSQ","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"177","text":"5. Komiotis C, et al. Genetic perspectives on TGA. Clin Neurol Neurosurg. 2025;258:109163.","guid":"Xk0O79MFRqS8u96ARnW6og","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"177","text":"6. Iyigundogdu I, et al. TGA and hippocampal diffusion restriction. Acta Neurol Belg. 2024;124(3):943-947.","guid":"wJ40q78fQHCgK9pjK9GVRQ","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"177","text":"7. Faust JS, et al. TGA: ED evaluation and management. Emerg Med Pract. 2016;18(8 Suppl):S1-S2.","guid":"e4Bkr02FTC-I6T2Pzdn5lw","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":184,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Neurología","filename":"Amnesia_Global_Transitoria","id":"map_1385","resolved_references":[]}